---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = "April 2026"; 
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Shakil Traders Limited">
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="bg-white p-8 md:p-16 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-slate-500 mb-8 italic text-sm">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

        <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 italic">1. Introduction</h2>
            <p>
              Welcome to the Privacy Policy of <strong>SHAKIL TRADERS LIMITED</strong> ("we", "us", or "our"). 
              We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This policy informs you 
              how we look after your personal data when you visit our website or engage with our wholesale services.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4">
              <strong>Shakil Traders Limited</strong> is the controller and responsible for your personal data 
              (Company Number: 13318529). Our registered office is located at 101 Whitechapel High Street, London, E1 7RA.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 italic">2. The Data We Collect</h2>
            <p>We may collect, use, and store different kinds of personal data about you, including:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-4">
              <li><strong>Identity Data:</strong> Name, business title, and company name.</li>
              <li><strong>Contact Data:</strong> Email address, telephone numbers, and delivery/billing addresses.</li>
              <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, and location data when using our website.</li>
              <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information about how you use our website and services.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 italic">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
            <p>We use your data only when the law allows us to. Most commonly, we use your data for:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-4">
              <li>Processing your wholesale orders and managing deliveries.</li>
              <li>Responding to inquiries sent via our contact forms.</li>
              <li>Complying with legal and regulatory obligations in the UK.</li>
              <li>Improving our website and business offerings.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 italic">4. Data Sharing</h2>
            <p>
              We do not sell your data. We may share your information with trusted third parties such as:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-4">
              <li>Logistics and delivery partners to fulfill your orders.</li>
              <li>Professional advisers (lawyers, bankers, auditors).</li>
              <li>HM Revenue & Customs (HMRC) and other UK regulatory authorities.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 italic">5. Data Security</h2>
            <p>
              We have put in place appropriate security measures to prevent your personal data from being 
              accidentally lost, used, or accessed in an unauthorized way. Access to your personal data 
              is limited to employees and partners who have a business need to know.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 italic">6. Your Legal Rights</h2>
            <p>
              Under UK data protection laws, you have rights including:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-4">
              <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of your personal data.</li>
              <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Request that we correct inaccurate data.</li>
              <li><strong>Erasure:</strong> Request that we delete your data (the "right to be forgotten").</li>
              <li><strong>Object:</strong> Object to processing of your data for direct marketing.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 mt-12">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide">Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy or our data practices, please contact us:</p>
            <div class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">
              <p>Email: sales@shakiltraders.com</p>
              <p>Post: 101 Whitechapel High Street, London, E1 7RA</p>
              <p>Attention: Data Privacy Lead</p>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Back to home link -->
      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/" class="text-green-600 hover:underline font-medium">&larr; Return to Home Page</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>